{"tid":758956,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾馬利炮轟舊東家：尼馬才是PSG「大佬」","createTime":"2018-07-28T07:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T08:59:11.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1cc8f79967e70cea45a6a81345c385dd3ce29b","tid":758956,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"艾馬利即將迎來自己執教阿仙奴的第一個賽季，但在賽季開始前，他卻又炮轟舊東家巴黎聖日耳門。他稱：「那支球隊不屬於自己，球隊『大佬』是尼馬。」<br />\n<br />\n　　艾馬利指：「在每間球會裡，你都要清楚自己扮演的角色是甚麼，也要清楚你給球隊其他成員分配的角色是甚麼。在我看來，巴黎聖日耳門的『大佬』叫尼馬。這種『大佬』地位需要一段時間來鞏固，在曼城是哥迪奧拿，在巴黎聖日耳門，卻必須是尼馬。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我不記得此前我又沒有說過這事，但是在我看來，在我的執教生涯中，我一直希望能獲得屬於我的執教方式，以及對我的支持，也希望能給球隊帶來良好的精神狀態，能給好球員們注入能量。」"},{"pid":"1fddd840689b123ece0b18257affa7331309c935","tid":758956,"uid":99642,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"條友仲好意思講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21dfaa5a53352524ba9473318a2ca544d9b2dda8","tid":758956,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:13:09.000Z","msg":"大佬就嚟走佬"},{"pid":"a259421f71b2ed5fffb63a45535837e314f77011","tid":758956,"uid":158613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"PSG大佬已經係包皮"},{"pid":"48b4bfb42699132718dd5f41721546903e459973","tid":758956,"uid":25231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T08:47:16.000Z","msg":"一見到球隊大佬哩啲字眼就以為係nineup報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8696ca80d25b4ed96bef0cd85ae15e2e54ff15b4","tid":758956,"uid":60982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48b4bfb42699132718dd5f41721546903e459973","tid":758956,"uid":25231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T08:47:16.000Z","msg":"一見到球隊大佬哩啲字眼就以為係nineup報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=